WEBVTT

00:00.439 --> 00:04.009
One of the most famous and highest achieving couples in the world,...

00:04.575 --> 00:06.306
...wealthy beyond imagination,...

00:06.586 --> 00:09.065
...Bill and Melinda Gates met at Microsoft,...

00:09.361 --> 00:11.246
...where they're best known as a power couple...

00:11.524 --> 00:13.656
...for the work of their charitable foundation.

00:14.055 --> 00:17.207
The news that they're planning to separate came out of the blue.

00:17.451 --> 00:18.965
They both tweeted a statement.

00:19.552 --> 00:22.844
"After a great deal of thought and a lot of work on our relationship,...

00:23.159 --> 00:25.404
...we've made the decision to end our marriage."

00:25.712 --> 00:28.884
The couple will continue to work together at their foundation,...

00:29.062 --> 00:32.524
...but they say "we no longer believe we can grow together as a couple...

00:32.811 --> 00:34.805
...in this next phase of our lives."

00:38.733 --> 00:40.475
The Bill and Melinda Gates Foundation...

00:40.721 --> 00:43.436
...has had a huge impact on the world of philanthropy...

00:43.746 --> 00:47.446
...with billions spent fighting causes such as infectious diseases...

00:47.761 --> 00:50.038
...and encouraging vaccinations in children.

00:50.485 --> 00:53.080
Bill and Melinda Gates are presenting a united front...

00:53.236 --> 00:54.683
...on the matter of their divorce...

00:55.009 --> 00:57.546
...and the same is likely to apply to their foundation,...

00:57.733 --> 01:02.640
...a global force for good even if their individual roles drift apart.

01:04.099 --> 01:07.301
Bill Gates, who founded Microsoft in 1975,...

01:07.496 --> 01:09.880
...is the world's fourth richest person...

01:10.101 --> 01:13.193
...with a net worth of more than 100 billion dollars.

01:13.655 --> 01:16.627
There's no word on any financial agreement between the couple.

01:16.969 --> 01:19.422
They've asked for space and privacy for their family...

01:19.654 --> 01:22.475
...as they begin to navigate their new lives.

